snippet.textDisplay: Dude,  another great job.  Thanks for putting out awesome music.  btw,  Just wanted to let you know that you've got three generations (four if you consider the age gaps) of fans in my family.  I stumbled across your talent from Glenn Fricker's channel with Moon On The Water. Completely hooked on your vocals.  I played the video for my Dad (70 years old), oldest son (25), daughter (21), and my two younger sons (16 & 13) , I'm 46 myself. Anyway, all of them were intensely watching the video and listening to your vocals when I notice that each one of them had the hair on their arms standing. They were all blown away to the point where my youngest son has had Moon on the Water going on repeat in his cell phone since the beginning of August. No other songs just that one song on repeat. Even my 70 year old dad watches the Moon on the Water video daily on his iPhone and downloaded it from itunes for all my kids.  Keep  up the great work. Someday the entire planet will appreciate your talent.
